claim.claim-text:
1. A toy vehicle wheel connection, comprising: 
(a) a toy vehicle wheel rim having an inner diameter and a center portion; 
(b) an insert sleeve having a radial outer wall and a radial inner wall, where said radial outer wall is permanently affixed to said inner diameter, and said radial inner wall has a plurality of radially outwardly extending tabs; 
(c) a vehicle element having a radial outer edge with an annular groove, said outer edge sized to fit within said inner wall, and said annular groove sized to provide a snug fit with said extending tabs;
